AMESGUIFrame.datacontrols

Class TestCaseWizardBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • AMESGUIFrame.datacontrols.TestCaseWizardBuilder

  • public class TestCaseWizardBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    A builder to centralize choices about what type of panel we show, based on the TestCase being constructed. Consider all of the collections of JFrames the AMES gui shows as the 'TestCase Wizard'
